:: Get Job Offer {"position":"300,1000","size":"100,100"}

It's ''Day 1001'' of the job hunt. After another day of nothing but automated rejections and ghost listings, you're just about to close your laptop for the day when you get a text from your good friend Alex.

''Alex:'' "Hey! Long time no see! The team I'm apart of at Corazón is hiring! We need a software engineer that's worked with electronic health records.The company makes medical devices that help thousands of people and the pay is pretty great as well! Want me to refer you to my manager?"

-------
