:: User Health Data Privacy {"position":"1250,800","size":"100,100"}
"Isn't this basically selling our users' identities?" you ask. "With modern AI, 'anonymized' data can be re-identified in seconds by cross-referencing records."

''Manager:'' "Technically as long as we strip the personally identifiable information like names, SINs, and PHNs, we've met our regulatory obligations"

''CEO'' "Just try to focus on the fact that this 'donation' will give us the opportunity to save 10,000 lives."
-------
([[Ask More Questions->Selling User Data]])
([[Agree to do task->Agree to Sell User Data]])
([[Refuse to do task->Refuse to Sell User Data]])


